=== Release criteria ===

The following minimum criteria must be fulfilled before a new version may be released:

* The code coverage for blocks must be at least 80%
* No findbugs warnings
* No stoppers
* All bugs and enhancements must be evaluated

Please send your ideas for improvement or contributions to discuss forum. Bugs or feature requests should be reported in the Issues.